- folder that contains helm charts to be targeted
- Chart.yaml
- helm template my-charts

- helm install local-charts my-charts -n my-test 
- helm uninstall local-charts my-charts -n my-test

- .Release.Name - the local name for installation
- .Chart.Name - the project/ repo name

- helm package --help
- helm package my-charts
- NOTE will be packages according to version, not appVersion
- helm install local-charts node-express-chart-1.0.1.tgz
- helm repo index . (initiate index for yaml in current directory)
- helm repo add shiu-helms https://kahshiu.github.io/k-helm-charts/
- helm repo list
- helm search repo express
- helm install local-charts shiu-helms/node-express-chart
- helm create app-2